| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0722 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ecbcc81c-c813-5d7c-b3ed-d345f5ec0a12"
